		<div class="post" id="post-1261702">
		<div class="long">
			<div class="head">
									<div class="options">
						<a href="javascript:;" onclick="togglePostFold(event,1261702)" class="btn btn-default btn-small btn-sm">Fold</a>
					</div>
								<div class="title" id="post-title-1261702">
																		
															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/thedeadlymoose" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(732274); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=732274&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610204617" alt="thedeadlymoose" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=732274)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/thedeadlymoose" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(732274); return false;" >thedeadlymoose</a></span> <span class="odate time_1316417622 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">19 Sep 2011 07:33</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1261702">
									

<p>This is excellent. Upvoted.</p>
<p>That said, there's some places that need polish.</p>
<blockquote>
<p>He immediately hit the floor as a hail of bullets passed through the area he'd just been standing in.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>This sentence is pretty damn awkward.</p>
<blockquote>
<p>He crawled on his belly towards the good doctor's desk, even as Mann continued firing wildly, yelling the entire time.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>We don't need 'yelling the entire time', since you have the yelling directly after. Similarly&#8230;</p>
<blockquote>
<p>&quot;I DON'T CARE WHAT SCP-001 IS! I DON'T WANT TO KNOW WHAT THE ORIGIN OF THE FOUNDATION IS! WOULD YOU PEOPLE JUST LEAVE ME ALONE!&quot; Mann, a little unhinged,</p>
</blockquote>
<p>We can see he's a little unhinged, so you don't need to tell us that.</p>
<blockquote>
<p>Assigned me to some of the anomalous skips, that we didn't know what they were.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>This is also an awkward sentence, and I don't think Clef speaks that clumsily (though I could be wrong; if I am, this gets the 'dialogue pass').</p>
<blockquote>
<p>I made sure I was their top agent, Ukelele.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>Grammatically, this sounds like the GOC's top agent is always called Ukelele. Is this the case?</p>
<blockquote>
<p>&quot;Alto…Why?&quot;</p>
</blockquote>
<p>This is a bad line. It's overused cliche of a line for one, and it doesn't make sense in context. Almost any other line would be preferable.</p>
<p>The bullet spraying and hiding under the desk and the ranting are a bit excessively silly - I would have preferred it if it was more realistically played. Would make Mann's reaction have more impact (or, well, any impact beyond a chuckle). On the other hand, this is the least of my recommendations - it actually works fine for me, I just think it would have <em>more</em> impact done otherwise.</p>
<p>But yeah, I think this idea is great, and the idea that Clef = Bright is entertaining to no end (whether or not I believe it). And Clef coming to fuck with Mann after the O5s tell him all these Sekrits is also a great idea.</p>

							</div>

								
